# üè¶ Python Bank System
A beginner to intermediate level **Bank Management System** built using Python 
and Object-Oriented Programming.
## ‚úÖ Features- Account creation- Secure login using Account Number & PIN- Deposit and Withdraw money- Balance inquiry- Transaction history tracking- Persistent data storage using JSON
## üõ† Technologies Used- Python- JSON- OOP Concepts- Datetime Module
